Title: Stranger
Plot: When a girl who vanished four years ago reappears, she claims to have been imprisoned and sexually abused. Benson and Stabler look into the case and find themselves having to sort through what was fact and what the girl made up.
GuestStars: Ellen Woglom (Heather Hallander), Kate Baldwin (Erica Hallander), Natalia Payne (Nikki Hallander)
